abstract: >-
  ScriptBreak is a local-first screenplay breakdown studio in the Wasserman
  Filmmaker Suite. It parses Final Draft, Fountain, and PDF screenplays into
  scene breakdowns with exact page counts, auto-tagged elements, character
  and location bibles, shot lists, and a visual timeline, then exports
  self-executing AI prompt packs usable with any LLM and any video or image
  generator — with no API keys, accounts, or server.
